import {Component} from "react"
import {PageContainer,Container,Input,Form,LabelText,SelectOptions} from "./styledComponent"


 

class App extends Component {

    render(){
        return(
            <PageContainer>
                <Container>
                    <Input type="text"  />
                </Container>
                <Form>
                    <LabelText htmlFor = "fontinput">Font Style</LabelText>
                    <SelectOptions>
                        <option>hh</option>
                        <option>jhaj</option>
                    </SelectOptions>
                </Form>
            </PageContainer>
        )
    }
}

 

export default App
